which got rejected.

307
00:18:40,080 --> 00:18:43,240
Now you're stuck and
getting deported to your country !

308
00:18:43,320 --> 00:18:45,880
You decided to start a company here.
Thank god.

309
00:18:46,040 --> 00:18:49,080
