"get in line" to people,

447
00:27:10,920 --> 00:27:14,440
make sure they have
a line to stand in.

448
00:27:14,760 --> 00:27:17,720
Now, these are the only
pathways that exist.

449
00:27:17,840 --> 00:27:20,200
We should be having
a serious conversation

