I never know where a case will lead

475
00:28:56,840 --> 00:28:59,600
but I'll never stop
until it's solved.

476
00:28:59,760 --> 00:29:03,320
I treat people fairly
but I'm also ruthless.

477
00:29:03,560 --> 00:29:05,800
I can be quite intimidating
when I want.

478
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:10,200
Do you think he walked out of your car
and ran into a knife six times, Mike ?

479
00:29:10,280 --> 00:29:11,800
Run that by me again, Eric !

480
00:29:11,880 --> 00:29:15,360
You understand what that means !
Mark, I'm embarrassed for you.

481
00:29:15,440 --> 00:29:18,520
Kevin, I'm starting to have
a relationship now with you.

482
00:29:18,600 --> 00:29:21,360
Christopher, I could
kiss you on the mouth.

483
00:29:21,440 --> 00:29:23,240
Well, my, my, my, Danny.

484
00:29:23,320 --> 00:29:27,360
Well, my, my, my.
Well, my, my, my, you lying little...

485
00:29:28,000 --> 00:29:31,120
If it walks like a duck and quacks
like a duck, it's a duck.

486
00:29:31,320 --> 00:29:33,720
Don't monkey
with somebody else's monkey.

487
00:29:33,800 --> 00:29:36,680
There's a tooth fairy,
maybe there's a blood fairy.

488
00:29:36,760 --> 00:29:39,800
When I leave, I'll have
somebody's ass in my briefcase.

489
00:29:39,920 --> 00:29:44,440
I don't trust anybody. I don't trust my
mother and she's dead for 11 years.

490
00:29:46,480 --> 00:29:50,480
